Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.86,0:00:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得这样做很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.41,0:00:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为一个大人 你不觉得羞耻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.40,0:00:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是很认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.80,0:00:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种 这种小孩子的恶作剧 才没有时间奉陪…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许你践踏老爸的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.19,0:00:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那么讨厌的话 就一辈子讨厌好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.44,0:00:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就讨厌超自然吧 你就讨厌老爸吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.29,0:00:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.65,0:00:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又咋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.02,0:00:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我向小玛雅道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}不变的亚美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.51,0:02:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 亚美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早上好 玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.33,0:02:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 班会要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:02:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二垒手 游击手！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right！All right！All right！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right！All right！All right！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right！All…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.36,0:03:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个 到底在搞啥飞机啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜 眼镜 眼镜…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后 我在皆神神社内等你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你听说了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假货UFO的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假货UFO？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道是哪来的谁搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过确实是让一个UFO的仿制品飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们傻么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 是趁机借那个怪圈忽悠人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是杰作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说还有我们的学生真的上当了 追着那个假货UFO去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山脚那里不是有个牧场嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在那里用轻型卡车搞出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逊毙了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.82,0:04:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连真假都分不清的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就没资格当我们这里的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那个牧场的牛大量死亡的事情好像是真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量牛只死亡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.49,0:04:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么一说 他们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个也真够辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还准备了那种死牛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:04:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没干过那事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.71,0:05:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来有必要再去调查一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.22,0:05:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像前几天的尸体一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体内的血液基本上都被抽干了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这真是外星人干的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.65,0:05:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这单细胞大脑还是没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥…啥？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.41,0:05:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这明显极可能是恶作剧嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是自然死亡 也会有类似血液被抽干的现象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于器官会被拿走 可以解释成是动物所为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连那么简单的事情都不知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说想调查尸体的是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.71,0:05:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样没错啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:06:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不该往恶作剧的方向想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.64,0:06:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说是恶作剧的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这规模也太大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.55,0:06:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太迟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太迟了！太迟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太迟了！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.44,0:06:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美 还不回去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天快要黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅肯定是有什么急事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的回答吗 玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个洞 毫无疑问就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要一直默默思考到什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:06:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才开始就一直都是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.67,0:07:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道在想黑木的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你说什么呢 什么亚美的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别装蒜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是你们的班主任
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还没和好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有…和好什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文明！现在几点了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…大概6点左右吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.34,0:07:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.95,0:07:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.65,0:08:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想干啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你们住手吧 朋友之间怎么能决斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不允许！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得玛雅你说得太过了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美也是做过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 这个时候就要喝点冷饮什么的冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去买东西回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干啥呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前几日…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怪物到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 梢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.94,0:09:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀稍微被咬了一下罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐 这是神马啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.08,0:10:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.27,0:10:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.25,0:10:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用来弹琴和拿探测棒的手指啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.26,0:10:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懒懒散散搞毛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快天黑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥我们连这种事都要做…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没！什么都没说！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美的话还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:11:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美她 被拐走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美被拐走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.16,0:11:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁干的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那帮家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…是啥来着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那啥 经常能在南美目击到的 袭击家畜的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会蹦蹦跳跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好像确实有那个的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…是啥来着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 那种事我一点都不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.68,0:11:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chupa…Chupacha…Chupacha…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Chupacabra啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chupacabra？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:12:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在西班牙语中指的是「吸山羊血的东西」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从几年前在波多黎各首次被目击以来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.88,0:12:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中南美全境 最近连美国也有目击报告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一种未确认的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,频发的牛只可疑死亡事件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.41,0:12:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种死因 伤痕 还有那个外表
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无疑问 那就是Chupacabra
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西在这小镇里面也有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不赶紧的话亚美就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.44,0:12:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.78,0:12:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:49.05,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Chupacabra
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.52,0:12:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都上来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.86,0:12:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.86,0:12:56.97,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yes, sir！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:12:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.24,0:13:17.18,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}眼镜…眼镜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 亚美在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我真是个蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不知道她被抓到哪里去了 怎么去救她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是不是忘了一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JK！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧场里的牛全部都？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:13:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所有的都被吸干了血
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.53,0:14:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论发生什么 我都会保护好美风小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.86,0:14:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得好～可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 又有点兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.24,0:15:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美同学会在这种地…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成濑？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要大意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.80,0:15:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JK 亚美在哪个方向
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那边 直走 在那深处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 赶紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.64,0:16:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没完没了的 都不知道从哪涌出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就由我们把它们挡下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玛雅 亚美就暂时交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.82,0:16:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去 玛雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.28,0:16:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战斗结束以后 真想看看你们和好之后的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些如果是电影里的台词的话 就是你们的便当FLAG啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美！快醒来啊亚美！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.08,0:17:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美 之前的事情真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你父亲说了过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才要说对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.42,0:18:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了打你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.53,0:19:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢对我女儿出手 就是你气数的尽头了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.58,0:19:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.69,0:19:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备闪人了 两位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们 做到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.93,0:19:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 简直是超额完成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为要被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子…还活着…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.74,0:19:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.70,0:19:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就是警察的工作了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.81,0:20:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～还以为要挂掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没受什么大伤就真是万幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 不觉得有股怪味吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么一说又确实…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 那是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊大火啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.02,0:20:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧叫消防车来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.78,0:20:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的怪物尸体已经全部处理掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.74,0:20:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是寺内的尸体就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种程度的火估计骨头烧不干净
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 就让他们当成野狗的巢穴来处理掉好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就继续给我监视好校长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:20:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我才要说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太 太好了 我还以为你们要决斗了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说没那回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆神神社 是我和玛雅小时候和好的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.62,0:21:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么差不多要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.49,0:21:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.88,0:21:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.85,0:21:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥…如果你不介意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.74,0:21:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告诉我 之前那个「在窗外窥视的鲜红人脸」的真身吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢 看见那窥视的鲜红人脸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.64,0:21:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们战战兢兢地打开了窗户…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.84,0:23:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见证自己出生的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.08,0:23:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满着无数回忆的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.08,0:23:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.38,0:23:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于小时候住的房子的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.65,0:23:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.80,0:23:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.46,0:23:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.79,0:23:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.51,0:23:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哔哔～我的探测棒有反应了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.91,0:24:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是幽灵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.06,0:24:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 让我给它一记狠的「问候」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.65,0:24:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.88,0:24:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个孩子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.19,0:24:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世纪末超自然学院
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.36,0:24:11.02,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}标题中同样出现了下集人物的名字「明」，直译为「雪的光亮」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.36,0:24:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 雪之明
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.00,0:24:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然那是超自然…但不能撒手不管…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------OP----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.40,0:01:05.01,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}十年先の未来が 見える魔法をがあったらな...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.34,0:01:06.68,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}見上げた空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.77,0:01:15.49,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}追いかけ続ける程 逃げてく世界の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.68,0:01:20.20,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}悩まずいられるのにな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.65,0:01:25.10,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}時を切り裂くような速さで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.67,0:01:31.83,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}駆け抜けてく　流されてく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.84,0:01:34.98,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}空に揺らねながら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:43.03,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}僕らは飛び立とうとしてんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:47.84,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}さんざん見た未来地図と
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:54.34,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}折れた翼広げ 広げ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.35,0:01:59.87,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}今 始まろとしてんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.25,0:02:04.87,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}誰か呼ぶ声がする
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.15,0:02:14.18,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}暁を染めて　染めて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.40,0:01:05.01,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}要是有魔法能预见十年后的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.34,0:01:06.68,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我仰望天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.77,0:01:15.49,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}在这越是追寻 却离得越远的世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.68,0:01:20.20,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}本应充满烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.65,0:01:25.10,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}以仿若切开时间般的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.67,0:01:31.83,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}飞奔而去 顺流而下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.84,0:01:34.98,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即使只能在空中摇摆不定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:43.03,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我们正欲起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:47.84,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}展开早已熟读的未来地图
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:54.34,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}和那折断的羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.35,0:01:59.87,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}现在 一切就要开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.25,0:02:04.87,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}耳中传来谁人的呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.15,0:02:14.18,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}将那片晨光染尽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------ED----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.55,0:22:20.82,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}君だけのため　光る世界　ここにあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.85,0:22:33.35,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}幼い手で握りしめてた　失くさないよ　ぎゅっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.75,0:22:42.67,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}真っ白な願いを　君と追いかけで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.70,0:22:50.66,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}まだ迷い込む　寂しいげな夜だから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:59.89,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}あの日の面影を　見つけで　思い出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.17,0:23:04.67,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}君がいるから　どこでだって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.03,0:23:08.92,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}何度、転んでも　笑える
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.42,0:23:13.28,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}偶然だとか　必然だとか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.39,0:23:16.31,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}要らないほど　強く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.48,0:23:25.12,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}きっと輝く　思い出なら　君の側にだけ　あるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.60,0:23:33.54,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}大切な世界　離さないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.55,0:22:20.82,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}仅属于你的光辉世界 就在此处
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.85,0:22:33.35,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}紧握着你幼小的手 牢牢地不让它溜走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.75,0:22:42.67,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}纯白的心愿 与你共同追寻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.70,0:22:50.66,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}若是被踌躇包围 寂寞如水的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:59.89,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}请于记忆深处 再次寻回 那天的音容
